'''Micheline Cheirel''' (born '''Micheline Truyen'''; 12 April 1917 – 25 October 2002) was a 20th century French actress.

==Personal life== 
She was the second wife (of five) of the British actor [[John Loder (actor)|John Loder]], from 1936 until their divorce in 1941. They had one child. She appeared in some films made in the United States. She married the French actor [[Paul Meurisse]] in 1951, and that also ended in divorce.{{cn|date=July 2018}}

